{"id":1735094,"retrievedAt":"2026-07-21T12:47:15.081Z","response":{"adult":false,"backdrop_path":null,"belongs_to_collection":null,"budget":0,"genres":[],"homepage":"","id":1735094,"imdb_id":null,"origin_country":["US"],"original_language":"en","original_title":"Suamiku Paling Sweet","overview":"# My Husband is the Sweetest  The story follows Qisya Iriz (Mawar Rashid), a university graduate who is forced to become a temporary caregiver for Hafiey (Adik Nik Adam Mika), the grandson of her mother's friend, Madam Fathma (Liza Abdullah). Previous caregivers could not cope with Hafiey's mischievous behavior. Qisya accepts her mother's suggestion because it is only temporary. When stubborn Qisya meets Hafiey, chaos ensues. Hafiey's parents died in an accident. Because of this, Hafiey considers his uncle Izz Haikal (Syafiq Kyle) as his biological father. Izz is willing to do anything for Hafiey's happiness. After meeting Hafiey's caregiver, both Izz and Qisya's hearts often flutter. However, they pay no attention to the true meaning behind their racing hearts until an event occurs that changes both their fates. Qisya is forced to become the wife of Izz Haikal at a young age. Various emotions begin to cloud Qisya's heart. She is shocked, angry, and resentful.","popularity":0,"poster_path":"/7CoBFNHv9T3yMqzh3jJhKrvlOQh.jpg","production_companies":[],"production_countries":[],"release_date":"2016-01-01","revenue":0,"runtime":0,"softcore":false,"spoken_languages":[],"status":"Released","tagline":"","title":"Suamiku Paling Sweet","video":false,"vote_average":0,"vote_count":0,"alternative_titles":{"titles":[]},"credits":{"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":0,"id":1758116,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Mawar Rashid","original_name":"Mawar Rashid","popularity":0.1327,"profile_path":"/yyXzJbHfOHZKUFoiNEHewjcu8hV.jpg","cast_id":2,"character":"","credit_id":"6a5ebdde65863e9adde2f87e","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":1758117,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Syafiq